item.title: CVE-2019-5914|2024-08-04T20:09:23.617Z -- ntt%20docomo%2C%20inc. -- v20%20pro%20l-01j
item.description: V20 PRO L-01J software version L01J20c and L01J20d has a NULL pointer exception flaw that can be used by an attacker to cause the device to crash on the same network range via a specially crafted access point.
